  "description": "A close-up shot focuses on the interior of a vibrant purple tulip. The flower is captured from a unique, low-angle perspective, showcasing its delicate petals curling inwards. The center reveals a cluster of yellow and dark brown stamens and a light blue-green pistil. The background is a soft, blurred wash of green foliage, creating a bokeh effect. The image has a shallow depth of field, further emphasizing the flower's intricate details and isolating it from its surroundings. The petals exhibit subtle textures, and the lighting appears soft and diffused.",
